      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This specimen boasts a perfectly calibrated dual-VANOS system and individual throttle bodies for immediate throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock. Structural integrity is paramount; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the suspension maintains its original kinematic excellence. Finished in a concours-ready state with no mechanical lash or fluid seepage, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-division engineering.",
